## Limitations

The findings are based on available online sources and may not capture the full spectrum of opinions and data on the topic. The reliance on surveys and opinion pieces means that the conclusions drawn may be influenced by the biases inherent in these sources. Additionally, the complexity of individual motivations and the diversity within generational cohorts mean that broad generalizations may not apply to all young people. Further research, including qualitative studies and interviews, would provide a more nuanced understanding of the phenomenon.